p.strong: How Republicans Are Weaponizing Critical Race Theory Ahead of Midterms

section.p: Republicans hope that concerns about critical race theory can help them in the midterm elections. The issue has torn apart one Wisconsin suburb.

p.strong: Blackfeet Nation Mourns Longtime Leader Chief Earl Old Person

section.p: Over four days in Montana, members honored Chief Earl Old Person, who led the tribe and preserved its history for more than 60 years.

p.strong: Mohamed Noor Receives Shorter Sentence in Fatal Shooting of Justine Ruszczyk

section.p: Mohamed Noor shot a resident who had called 911 seeking help. His conviction was seen as a rare example of an officer facing serious consequences for an unjustified shooting.
